{
  "stem": "18102.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He told me for hours and days, because it didn't happen right away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Days on end, until finally he was one of the fortunate ones among some 5,000 or more-- no one knows the exact figure-- that received visa.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, if you received the visa, it was a visa for your entire family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So every time Sugihara issued one visa to Moshe Melamdovich he issued it to Moshe Melundelvich's wife, Fejgla Melamdovich and their son, [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Label ?] Melamdovich as well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, he-- he mentioned the fact that the council was a-- a kindly, young man, he said, but seemed to understand the plight of the Jews that were in the courtyard and around the home.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- he entered alone because they took turns going in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to sign papers, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there wasn't a great deal of conversation, because it was all done quite hurriedly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were so many waiting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you had to do the formalities as quickly as possible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in that moment, my father said, perhaps because here was a savior giving him a visa, or perhaps because he really saw the inside of Sugihara, he said to me, he looked like a person with a great deal of compassion.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, since then I know the story so much better.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I recall my father's words as a child to me, later saying that this was a compassionate man saving the lives of so many people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, at that time we didn't know that it would end up saving our lives.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was just a hope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We still had to get permission to leave Lithuania, in effect to leave Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
